description.en:
1) Usotsuki Ookami
Satsuki is a counselor at a prestigious boys' high school. In fact, she is an ordinary high school student. Though she wishes that it will not be revealed, Tsuburaya, a problem student of the school, hangs around her...?!

2) Miscalculation of the Little Demon
His Family is about reach as mine, but he is 9 years older and already turned me down. then why is he here again?

3) Together with Doggie
They are interested in me because of my face. I'm tired of younger boy's confessions but this dog like boy won't leave me alone ...

4) Deli Bunny Girl
Working in a cosplay cafe for bunny ear maniacs when I'm just a high schooler! He find outs, what should I do now?

5) Non-sugar Darling
We've been dating for 1 year now, but it looks like there is no love anymore.
